title: Question 15
description: Where can I find the list of the $BOND NFTs?

fields.title: Answer:
fields.value: $BOND is a contract for 200 (two hundred) fully compliant ERC-721 tokens minted by InfiNFT and viewable on OpenSea here: [https://opensea.io/storefront/barnbridge-non-fungible-token](https://opensea.io/storefront/barnbridge-non-fungible-token).
